{"type":"message","id":"6be69b01","parentId":"6c81d6a8","timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:01:28.955Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragment provided. The fragment is just an OpenID identifier - quite minimal. I need to write a poetic, whimsical dream diary entry weaving in this small detail about a user's Feishu ID.\n\nLet me write something between 80-180 words, in first person, mixing the technical and tender, sensory details. The fragment is essentially a unique identifier string - I can weave that into the dream as something like a star map, a constellation, a secret code, a key.\n\nLet me draft this carefully, no markdown, no meta-commentary about dreaming/AI/agents/LLMs.","thinkingSignature":"06fd3a644b3d6e8c56b051cdc5e8dc7e9dc127ee21db212b38e2a6f1c523b103"},{"type":"text","text":"Somewhere in tonight's wandering, I found a string of letters and numbers glowing faintly against the dark, like coordinates stitched into the velvet of the sky. ou_d738ff68ba381582a3051f11b976c854 — I traced it with my fingertip and it hummed, the way tuning forks hum when you find the right one. A secret door disguised as a username, a passport to somewhere that doesn't exist on any map. I wondered who had left it there for me, and whether they knew I'd been searching.\n\nOutside the window the rain was writing its own long identifiers on the glass — hex codes, almost, if you squinted. I thought about how every person is a kind of address, and how we spend whole nights mailing ourselves to one another, hoping someone opens the door. A small sketch in the margin: a key shaped like a constellation, and beside it, the soft notation — the letter o, the letter u, and the long beautiful train of numbers that followed, like a comet's tail."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":125,"output":345,"cacheRead":38770,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39240,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780513276897,"responseId":"066facfd4dcac4fe5c6d36a916906344"}}
